<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verification Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            color: #1F2937;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 0;
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
        }

        .card {
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .icon-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .icon-circle {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background-color: #EFF6FF;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .shield-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .content-body {
            padding: 0 40px 32px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111827;
            margin: 0 0 16px 0;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        p {
            color: #6B7280;
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0 0 32px 0;
        }

        .otp-wrapper {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px 0;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .otp-code {
            display: inline-block;
            /* background-color: #2563EB; */
            color: #000;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding-right: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
        }

        .timer-container {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 280px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .timer-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #DC2626;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: block;
        }

        .progress-track {
            width: 100%;
            height: 6px;
            background-color: #EFF6FF;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #2563EB;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transform-origin: left;
            -webkit-animation: countdown 120s linear forwards;
            animation: countdown 120s linear forwards;
        }

        @-webkit-keyframes countdown {
            0% {
                width: 100%;
            }

            100% {
                width: 0%;
            }
        }

        @keyframes countdown {
            0% {
                width: 100%;
            }

            100% {
                width: 0%;
            }
        }

        .footer-warning {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .warning-text {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6B7280;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .copyright-text {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 32px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="card">

            <div class="icon-header">
                <div class="icon-circle">
                    <span class="shield-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-body">
                <h1>Verification Code</h1>
                <p>Hello <%= name %>, please use the following One Time Password (OTP) to verify your identity.</p>

                <div class="otp-wrapper">
                    <span class="otp-code">
                        <%= otp %>
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="timer-container">
                    <span class="timer-label">Expires in 2 minutes</span>
                    <div class="progress-track">
                        <div class="progress-bar"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-warning">
                <p class="warning-text">
                    <strong>Don't share this code.</strong><br>
                    If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email. Someone else might have typed
                    your email address by mistake.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="copyright-text">
            &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Medi-Flow Inc.<br>
                Khulna, Bangladesh.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
